            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台特化(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4772:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4772\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4772-TW</a>)23日11:34股價下跌24.5元，報302.5元，跌幅7.49%，成交3,438張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台特化(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4772:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4772\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4772-TW</a>)所屬產業為化學工業，主要業務為半導體特氣及精密化學材料之製造與買賣。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲4.14%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲9.79%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-490 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-696 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+1 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+205 張</li> <li>融資增減：+466 張</li> <li>融券增減：-23 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
